org.itsnat.comp.button.normal

Interface ItsNatButtonNormal

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ItsNatButton, ItsNatComponent, ItsNatElementComponent, ItsNatUserData
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ItsNatFreeButtonNormal, ItsNatFreeButtonNormalLabel, ItsNatHTMLAnchor, ItsNatHTMLAnchorLabel, ItsNatHTMLButton, ItsNatHTMLButtonLabel, ItsNatHTMLInputButton, ItsNatHTMLInputButtonNormal, ItsNatHTMLInputImage, ItsNatHTMLInputReset, ItsNatHTMLInputSubmit

    public interface ItsNatButtonNormal
extends ItsNatButton
    Is the base interface of normal button components.

    By default this component type uses a javax.swing.DefaultButtonModel button model.
